{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841159768,"sessionID":"ses_287a0d953ffeprum1kjA3lYblB","part":{"id":"prt_d7861a9cb001A52vZUTDvGw4iV","messageID":"msg_d78603ca2001x1FZ8040o2wuIo","sessionID":"ses_287a0d953ffeprum1kjA3lYblB","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-5a4cbc7d9f464d419a41ecab010be69f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n\n**Module**: `pkg/apis`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: S\n**Purpose**: Define shared types and constants for CRD resources in the AgentCube project.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── constants.go               # Shared constants\n        ├── types.go                   # Core type definitions (AgentRuntime + CodeInterpreter + Sandbox types)\n        ├── register.go                # Scheme registration\n        ├── doc.go                     # Package documentation\n        ├── deepcopy.go                # DeepCopy methods (generated)\n        └── types_test.go              # Unit tests\n```\n\n### Design Principles\n\n1. **Single Source of Truth**: Shared types and constants defined once in `v1alpha1` package\n2. **Type Safety**: Strong typing for all runtime configurations\n3. **Extensibility**: Easy to add new runtime types and constants\n4. **Validation**: Kubernetes CRD validation enforces enum constraints\n5. **Backward Compatibility**: Constants support graceful migration to new values\n\n### Component Interactions\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                   pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1                │\n│                                                              │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  constants.go - Shared Constants                     │  │\n│  │  • DefaultTimeouts (DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout)     │  │\n│  │  • RuntimeTypes (RuntimeTypePython, etc.)            │  │\n│  │  • ResourceLimits (DefaultCPULimit, DefaultMemoryLimit)│ │\n│  │  • ProtocolTypes (ProtocolTCP, etc.)                 │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                          ↓                                  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  types.go - Shared Types                             │  │\n│  │  • SandboxContainerResources                         │  │\n│  │  • SandboxEnvVar                                     │  │\n│  │  • SandboxEnvVarSource                               │  │\n│  │  • SandboxFieldRef                                   │  │\n│  │  • SandboxConfigMapKeyRef                            │  │\n│  │  • SandboxSecretKeyRef                               │  │\n│  │  • SandboxResourceList                               │  │\n│  │  • SandboxContainerPort                              │  │\n│  │  • SandboxVolumeMount                                │  │\n│  │  • SandboxVolume                                     │  │\n│  │  • SandboxEmptyDirVolumeSource                       │  │\n│  │  • SandboxConfigMapVolumeSource                      │  │\n│  │  • SandboxSecretVolumeSource                         │  │\n│  │  • SandboxPersistentVolumeClaimVolumeSource          │  │\n│  │  • SandboxKeyToPath                                  │  │\n│  │  • SandboxResources                                  │  │\n│  │  • SandboxProbe                                      │  │\n│  │  • SandboxProbeHandler                               │  │\n│  │  • SandboxExecAction                                 │  │\n│  │  • SandboxTCPSocketAction                            │  │\n│  │  • SandboxHTTPGetAction                              │  │\n│  │  • SandboxHTTPHeader                                 │  │\n│  │  • SandboxSecurityContext                            │  │\n│  │  • SandboxCapabilities                               │  │\n│  │  • SandboxSeccompProfile                             │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                          ↓                                  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  AgentRuntime Types                                  │  │\n│  │  • AgentRuntime                                     │  │\n│  │  • AgentRuntimeSpec                                  │  │\n│  │  • AgentRuntimeStatus                                │  │\n│  │  • AgentRuntimeList                                  │  │\n│  │  • SandboxTemplate                                   │  │\n│  │  • SandboxMetadata                                   │  │\n│  │  • SandboxPodSpec                                    │  │\n│  │  • SandboxContainer                                  │  │\n│  │  • SandboxAffinity                                   │  │\n│  │  • SandboxNodeAffinity                               │  │\n│  │  • SandboxPodAffinity                                │  │\n│  │  • SandboxPodAntiAffinity                            │  │\n│  │  • SandboxToleration                                 │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│                          ↓                                  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  CodeInterpreter Types                               │  │\n│  │  • CodeInterpreter                                   │  │\n│  │  • CodeInterpreterSpec                                │  │\n│  │  • CodeInterpreterStatus                              │  │\n│  │  • CodeInterpreterList                                │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n                          │ Imported by\n                          ↓\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Controllers & Consumers                       │\n│  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐              │\n│  │  AgentRuntime    │  │ CodeInterpreter  │              │\n│  │  Controller      │  │ Controller       │              │\n│  └──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### Constants\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants.go`\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport \"time\"\n\nconst (\n\tDefaultCodeExecutionTimeout = 5 * time.Minute\n\n\tRuntimeTypePython      = \"python\"\n\tRuntimeTypeJavaScript  = \"javascript\"\n\tRuntimeTypeTypeScript  = \"typescript\"\n\tRuntimeTypeGo          = \"go\"\n\n\tProtocolTCP  = \"TCP\"\n\tProtocolUDP  = \"UDP\"\n\tProtocolSCTP = \"SCTP\"\n\n\tDefaultCPULimit    = \"1\"\n\tDefaultMemoryLimit = \"1Gi\"\n\n\tDefaultCPURequest    = \"100m\"\n\tDefaultMemoryRequest = \"128Mi\"\n\n\tSeccompProfileTypeRuntimeDefault = \"RuntimeDefault\"\n\tSeccompProfileTypeUnconfined     = \"Unconfined\"\n\tSeccompProfileTypeLocalhost      = \"Localhost\"\n\n\tSessionTimeoutDefault       = 15 * time.Minute\n\tMaxSessionDurationDefault   = 8 * time.Hour\n)\n```\n\n### Shared Types\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go`\n\nThe following types are shared between AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter:\n\n#### Resource Types\n\n```go\ntype SandboxContainerResources struct {\n\tLimits   SandboxResourceList `json:\"limits,omitempty\"`\n\tRequests SandboxResourceList `json:\"requests,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxResourceList struct {\n\tCPU              string `json:\"cpu,omitempty\"`\n\tMemory           string `json:\"memory,omitempty\"`\n\tEphemeralStorage string `json:\"ephemeralStorage,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxResources struct {\n\tLimits   SandboxResourceList `json:\"limits,omitempty\"`\n\tRequests SandboxResourceList `json:\"requests,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### Environment Variable Types\n\n```go\ntype SandboxEnvVar struct {\n\tName      string                `json:\"name\"`\n\tValue     string                `json:\"value,omitempty\"`\n\tValueFrom *SandboxEnvVarSource  `json:\"valueFrom,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxEnvVarSource struct {\n\tFieldRef        *SandboxFieldRef        `json:\"fieldRef,omitempty\"`\n\tConfigMapKeyRef *SandboxConfigMapKeyRef `json:\"configMapKeyRef,omitempty\"`\n\tSecretKeyRef    *SandboxSecretKeyRef    `json:\"secretKeyRef,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxFieldRef struct {\n\tFieldPath string `json:\"fieldPath\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxConfigMapKeyRef struct {\n\tName     string `json:\"name\"`\n\tKey      string `json:\"key\"`\n\tOptional *bool   `json:\"optional,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxSecretKeyRef struct {\n\tName     string `json:\"name\"`\n\tKey      string `json:\"key\"`\n\tOptional *bool   `json:\"optional,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### Container Types\n\n```go\ntype SandboxContainerPort struct {\n\tName          string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n\tContainerPort int32  `json:\"containerPort\"`\n\tProtocol      string `json:\"protocol,omitempty\"`\n\tHostPort      int32  `json:\"hostPort,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### Volume Types\n\n```go\ntype SandboxVolumeMount struct {\n\tName      string `json:\"name\"`\n\tMountPath string `json:\"mountPath\"`\n\tSubPath   string `json:\"subPath,omitempty\"`\n\tReadOnly  bool   `json:\"readOnly,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxVolume struct {\n\tName                   string                                   `json:\"name\"`\n\tEmptyDir               *SandboxEmptyDirVolumeSource             `json:\"emptyDir,omitempty\"`\n\tConfigMap              *SandboxConfigMapVolumeSource            `json:\"configMap,omitempty\"`\n\tSecret                 *SandboxSecretVolumeSource               `json:\"secret,omitempty\"`\n\tPersistentVolumeClaim  *SandboxPersistentVolumeClaimVolumeSource `json:\"persistentVolumeClaim,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxEmptyDirVolumeSource struct {\n\tSizeLimit string `json:\"sizeLimit,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxConfigMapVolumeSource struct {\n\tName     string             `json:\"name\"`\n\tOptional *bool              `json:\"optional,omitempty\"`\n\tItems    []SandboxKeyToPath `json:\"items,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxSecretVolumeSource struct {\n\tSecretName string             `json:\"secretName\"`\n\tOptional   *bool              `json:\"optional,omitempty\"`\n\tItems      []SandboxKeyToPath `json:\"items,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxPersistentVolumeClaimVolumeSource struct {\n\tClaimName string `json:\"claimName\"`\n\tReadOnly  bool   `json:\"readOnly,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxKeyToPath struct {\n\tKey  string  `json:\"key\"`\n\tPath string  `json:\"path\"`\n\tMode *int32  `json:\"mode,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### Probe Types\n\n```go\ntype SandboxProbe struct {\n\tSandboxProbeHandler `json:\",inline\"`\n\tInitialDelaySeconds int32 `json:\"initialDelaySeconds,omitempty\"`\n\tTimeoutSeconds      int32 `json:\"timeoutSeconds,omitempty\"`\n\tPeriodSeconds       int32 `json:\"periodSeconds,omitempty\"`\n\tSuccessThreshold    int32 `json:\"successThreshold,omitempty\"`\n\tFailureThreshold    int32 `json:\"failureThreshold,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxProbeHandler struct {\n\tExec     *SandboxExecAction    `json:\"exec,omitempty\"`\n\tTCPSocket *SandboxTCPSocketAction `json:\"tcpSocket,omitempty\"`\n\tHTTPGet   *SandboxHTTPGetAction   `json:\"httpGet,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxExecAction struct {\n\tCommand []string `json:\"command\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxTCPSocketAction struct {\n\tPort k8sutil.IntOrString `json:\"port\"`\n\tHost string              `json:\"host,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxHTTPGetAction struct {\n\tPort        k8sutil.IntOrString `json:\"port\"`\n\tHost        string              `json:\"host,omitempty\"`\n\tPath        string              `json:\"path,omitempty\"`\n\tScheme      string              `json:\"scheme,omitempty\"`\n\tHTTPHeaders []SandboxHTTPHeader `json:\"httpHeaders,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxHTTPHeader struct {\n\tName  string `json:\"name\"`\n\tValue string `json:\"value\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### Security Types\n\n```go\ntype SandboxSecurityContext struct {\n\tRunAsUser                *int64                 `json:\"runAsUser,omitempty\"`\n\tRunAsGroup               *int64                 `json:\"runAsGroup,omitempty\"`\n\tRunAsNonRoot             *bool                  `json:\"runAsNonRoot,omitempty\"`\n\tReadOnlyRootFilesystem   *bool                  `json:\"readOnlyRootFilesystem,omitempty\"`\n\tAllowPrivilegeEscalation *bool                  `json:\"allowPrivilegeEscalation,omitempty\"`\n\tCapabilities             *SandboxCapabilities    `json:\"capabilities,omitempty\"`\n\tSeccompProfile           *SandboxSeccompProfile  `json:\"seccompProfile,omitempty\"`\n\tPrivileged               *bool                  `json:\"privileged,omitempty\"`\n\tProcMount                string                 `json:\"procMount,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxCapabilities struct {\n\tAdd  []string `json:\"add,omitempty\"`\n\tDrop []string `json:\"drop,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxSeccompProfile struct {\n\tType             string `json:\"type\"`\n\tLocalhostProfile string `json:\"localhostProfile,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### CRD Validation\n\n#### CodeInterpreter Runtime Enum\n\n```go\n// +kubebuilder:default=\"python\"\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=python;javascript;typescript;go\n// +optional\nRuntime string `json:\"runtime,omitempty\"`\n```\n\nSupported values:\n- `python`\n- `javascript`\n- `typescript`\n- `go`\n\n#### Timeout Format\n\n```go\n// +kubebuilder:default=\"5m\"\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Type=string\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Format=duration\n// +optional\nTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"timeout,omitempty\"`\n```\n\nValid duration formats:\n- `5m` (5 minutes)\n- `1h` (1 hour)\n- `30s` (30 seconds)\n- `1h30m` (1 hour 30 minutes)\n\n#### Port Validation\n\n```go\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=1\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Maximum=65535\nContainerPort int32 `json:\"containerPort\"`\n```\n\nPort range: 1-65535\n\n#### Protocol Enum\n\n```go\n// +kubebuilder:default=TCP\n// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=TCP;UDP;SCTP\n// +optional\nProtocol string `json:\"protocol,omitempty\"`\n```\n\nSupported values:\n- `TCP`\n- `UDP`\n- `SCTP`\n\n### Constants Usage\n\n#### Default Values in Controllers\n\n```go\nimport (\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nfunc applyDefaults(ci *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter) {\n\tif ci.Spec.Runtime == \"\" {\n\t\tci.Spec.Runtime = v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython\n\t}\n\tif ci.Spec.Timeout == nil {\n\t\tci.Spec.Timeout = &metav1.Duration{\n\t\t\tDuration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n#### Resource Defaults\n\n```go\nfunc applyResourceDefaults(resources *v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources) {\n\tif resources == nil {\n\t\tresources = &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{}\n\t}\n\tif resources.Requests.CPU == \"\" {\n\t\tresources.Requests.CPU = v1alpha1.DefaultCPURequest\n\t}\n\tif resources.Requests.Memory == \"\" {\n\t\tresources.Requests.Memory = v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryRequest\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Validation Errors\n\n#### Invalid Runtime Type\n\n```go\nfunc validateRuntimeType(runtime string) error {\n\tvalidRuntimes := map[string]bool{\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython:     true,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeJavaScript: true,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeTypeScript: true,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeGo:         true,\n\t}\n\n\tif !validRuntimes[runtime] {\n\t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"invalid runtime type: %s, must be one of: python, javascript, typescript, go\", runtime)\n\t}\n\treturn nil\n}\n```\n\n#### Invalid Timeout Format\n\n```go\nfunc validateTimeout(timeout *metav1.Duration) error {\n\tif timeout == nil {\n\t\treturn nil\n\t}\n\n\tif timeout.Duration <= 0 {\n\t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"timeout must be positive, got: %v\", timeout.Duration)\n\t}\n\n\tif timeout.Duration > 24*time.Hour {\n\t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"timeout cannot exceed 24 hours, got: %v\", timeout.Duration)\n\t}\n\n\treturn nil\n}\n```\n\n#### Invalid Port Range\n\n```go\nfunc validatePort(port int32) error {\n\tif port < 1 || port > 65535 {\n\t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"port must be between 1 and 65535, got: %d\", port)\n\t}\n\treturn nil\n}\n```\n\n### Client-Go Error Handling\n\n```go\nimport (\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n)\n\nci := &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n\tSpec: v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n\t\tImage:   \"python:3.11-slim\",\n\t\tRuntime: v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython,\n\t},\n}\n\ncreatedCi, err := client.CodeInterpreters(namespace).Create(ctx, ci, metav1.CreateOptions{})\nif err != nil {\n\tswitch {\n\tcase errors.IsAlreadyExists(err):\n\t\tlog.Warn(\"CodeInterpreter already exists\")\n\tcase errors.IsInvalid(err):\n\t\tlog.Errorf(\"Invalid CodeInterpreter spec: %v\", err)\n\tcase errors.IsForbidden(err):\n\t\tlog.Errorf(\"Permission denied: %v\", err)\n\tdefault:\n\t\tlog.Errorf(\"Failed to create CodeInterpreter: %v\", err)\n\t}\n\treturn err\n}\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/constants_test.go` (to be created)\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1_test\n\nimport (\n\t\"testing\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nfunc TestDefaultTimeout(t *testing.T) {\n\tif v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout != 5*time.Minute {\n\t\tt.Errorf(\"Expected default timeout 5m, got %v\", v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout)\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestRuntimeTypes(t *testing.T) {\n\truntimes := []string{\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeJavaScript,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeTypeScript,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeGo,\n\t}\n\n\tfor _, runtime := range runtimes {\n\t\tif runtime == \"\" {\n\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Runtime type should not be empty\")\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestProtocolTypes(t *testing.T) {\n\tprotocols := []string{\n\t\tv1alpha1.ProtocolTCP,\n\t\tv1alpha1.ProtocolUDP,\n\t\tv1alpha1.ProtocolSCTP,\n\t}\n\n\tfor _, protocol := range protocols {\n\t\tif protocol == \"\" {\n\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Protocol type should not be empty\")\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestResourceLimits(t *testing.T) {\n\tif v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit == \"\" {\n\t\tt.Error(\"DefaultCPULimit should not be empty\")\n\t}\n\n\tif v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit == \"\" {\n\t\tt.Error(\"DefaultMemoryLimit should not be empty\")\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestSeccompProfileTypes(t *testing.T) {\n\tprofiles := []string{\n\t\tv1alpha1.SeccompProfileTypeRuntimeDefault,\n\t\tv1alpha1.SeccompProfileTypeUnconfined,\n\t\tv1alpha1.SeccompProfileTypeLocalhost,\n\t}\n\n\tfor _, profile := range profiles {\n\t\tif profile == \"\" {\n\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Seccomp profile type should not be empty\")\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go` (existing)\n\nExisting tests cover:\n- AgentRuntime types\n- CodeInterpreter types\n- Sandbox types\n- DeepCopy functionality\n- JSON serialization\n- Scheme registration\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/client_integration_test.go`\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1_test\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"testing\"\n\n\t. \"github.com/onsi/ginkgo/v2\"\n\t. \"github.com/onsi/gomega\"\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n\t\"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/scheme\"\n\n\truntimev1alpha1 \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nvar _ = Describe(\"Shared Types Integration\", func() {\n\tIt(\"should use shared SandboxContainerResources in CodeInterpreter\", func(ctx SpecContext) {\n\t\tci := &runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n\t\t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n\t\t\t\tName:      \"test-ci\",\n\t\t\t\tNamespace: \"default\",\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t\tSpec: runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n\t\t\t\tImage: \"python:3.11-slim\",\n\t\t\t\tResources: &runtimev1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{\n\t\t\t\t\tLimits: runtimev1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tCPU:    runtimev1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit,\n\t\t\t\t\t\tMemory: runtimev1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit,\n\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tif ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU != runtimev1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit {\n\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Expected CPU limit %s, got %s\", runtimev1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit, ci.Spec.Resources.Limits.CPU)\n\t\t}\n\t})\n\n\tIt(\"should use shared SandboxEnvVar in both CRDs\", func(ctx SpecContext) {\n\t\tenv := runtimev1alpha1.SandboxEnvVar{\n\t\t\tName:  \"API_KEY\",\n\t\t\tValueFrom: &runtimev1alpha1.SandboxEnvVarSource{\n\t\t\t\tSecretKeyRef: &runtimev1alpha1.SandboxSecretKeyRef{\n\t\t\t\t\tName: \"api-secret\",\n\t\t\t\t\tKey:  \"key\",\n\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tif env.ValueFrom.SecretKeyRef.Name != \"api-secret\" {\n\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Expected secret name api-secret, got %s\", env.ValueFrom.SecretKeyRef.Name)\n\t\t}\n\t})\n})\n```\n\n### Validation Tests\n\n```go\nfunc TestRuntimeTypeValidation(t *testing.T) {\n\tvalidRuntimes := []string{\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeJavaScript,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeTypeScript,\n\t\tv1alpha1.RuntimeTypeGo,\n\t}\n\n\tfor _, runtime := range validRuntimes {\n\t\terr := validateRuntimeType(runtime)\n\t\tif err != nil {\n\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Runtime type %s should be valid, got error: %v\", runtime, err)\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tinvalidRuntime := \"rust\"\n\terr := validateRuntimeType(invalidRuntime)\n\tif err == nil {\n\t\tt.Errorf(\"Runtime type %s should be invalid\", invalidRuntime)\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestTimeoutValidation(t *testing.T) {\n\ttests := []struct {\n\t\tname        string\n\t\ttimeout     *metav1.Duration\n\t\texpectError bool\n\t}{\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"valid timeout\",\n\t\t\ttimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 5 * time.Minute},\n\t\t\texpectError: false,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"nil timeout\",\n\t\t\ttimeout:     nil,\n\t\t\texpectError: false,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"zero timeout\",\n\t\t\ttimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 0},\n\t\t\texpectError: true,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"negative timeout\",\n\t\t\ttimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: -5 * time.Minute},\n\t\t\texpectError: true,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"timeout exceeds max\",\n\t\t\ttimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 25 * time.Hour},\n\t\t\texpectError: true,\n\t\t},\n\t}\n\n\tfor _, tt := range tests {\n\t\tt.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n\t\t\terr := validateTimeout(tt.timeout)\n\t\t\tif tt.expectError && err == nil {\n\t\t\t\tt.Error(\"Expected error, got nil\")\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\tif !tt.expectError && err != nil {\n\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Expected no error, got: %v\", err)\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t})\n\t}\n}\n\nfunc TestPortValidation(t *testing.T) {\n\ttests := []struct {\n\t\tname        string\n\t\tport        int32\n\t\texpectError bool\n\t}{\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"valid port\",\n\t\t\tport:        8080,\n\t\t\texpectError: false,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"port too low\",\n\t\t\tport:        0,\n\t\t\texpectError: true,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"port too high\",\n\t\t\tport:        65536,\n\t\t\texpectError: true,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"port boundary min\",\n\t\t\tport:        1,\n\t\t\texpectError: false,\n\t\t},\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tname:        \"port boundary max\",\n\t\t\tport:        65535,\n\t\t\texpectError: false,\n\t\t},\n\t}\n\n\tfor _, tt := range tests {\n\t\tt.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n\t\t\terr := validatePort(tt.port)\n\t\t\tif tt.expectError && err == nil {\n\t\t\t\tt.Error(\"Expected error, got nil\")\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\tif !tt.expectError && err != nil {\n\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"Expected no error, got: %v\", err)\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t})\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n## Integration Points\n\n### With AgentRuntime Controller\n\n```go\nimport (\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n)\n\nfunc (r *AgentRuntimeReconciler) reconcilePod(ar *v1alpha1.AgentRuntime) error {\n\tpod := &corev1.Pod{\n\t\tSpec: corev1.PodSpec{\n\t\t\tContainers: []corev1.Container{\n\t\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\t\tResources: corev1.ResourceRequirements{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tLimits: corev1.ResourceList{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcorev1.ResourceCPU: resource.MustParse(\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tv1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t),\n\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t},\n\t}\n\treturn nil\n}\n```\n\n### With CodeInterpreter Controller\n\n```go\nfunc (r *CodeInterpreterReconciler) reconcileInterpreter(ci *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter) error {\n\tif ci.Spec.Timeout == nil {\n\t\tci.Spec.Timeout = &metav1.Duration{\n\t\t\tDuration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tif ci.Spec.Runtime == \"\" {\n\t\tci.Spec.Runtime = v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython\n\t}\n\treturn nil\n}\n```\n\n### With Session Router\n\n```go\nfunc (r *Router) getInterpreterTimeout(ci *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter) time.Duration {\n\tif ci.Spec.Timeout != nil {\n\t\treturn ci.Spec.Timeout.Duration\n\t}\n\treturn v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout\n}\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### Go Dependencies\n\n```go\nimport (\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/intstr\"\n\t\"time\"\n)\n```\n\n### Build Tools\n\n- `controller-gen`: v0.17.2 (for CRD generation)\n- `k8s.io/code-generator`: v0.34.1 (for client-go generation)\n\n### Makefile Targets\n\n| Target | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `gen-crd` | Generate CRD manifests |\n| `gen-client` | Generate client-go library |\n| `generate` | Generate all code (CRD + deepcopy) |\n| `gen-all` | `generate` + `gen-client` |\n| `gen-check` | Verify generated code is up-to-date |\n\n## Documentation\n\n### Example Usage with Constants\n\n```go\npackage main\n\nimport (\n\t\"time\"\n\t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\nfunc createPythonInterpreter() *v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter {\n\treturn &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n\t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n\t\t\tName:      \"python-interpreter\",\n\t\t\tNamespace: \"default\",\n\t\t},\n\t\tSpec: v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{\n\t\t\tImage: \"python:3.11-slim\",\n\t\t\tRuntime: v1alpha1.RuntimeTypePython,\n\t\t\tTimeout: &metav1.Duration{\n\t\t\t\tDuration: v1alpha1.DefaultCodeExecutionTimeout,\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t\tResources: &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{\n\t\t\t\tLimits: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n\t\t\t\t\tCPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit,\n\t\t\t\t\tMemory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit,\n\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\tRequests: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n\t\t\t\t\tCPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPURequest,\n\t\t\t\t\tMemory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryRequest,\n\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t},\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n### Shared Type Reuse\n\n```go\nfunc createContainerWithDefaults() v1alpha1.SandboxContainer {\n\treturn v1alpha1.SandboxContainer{\n\t\tName:  \"interpreter\",\n\t\tImage: \"python:3.11-slim\",\n\t\tResources: &v1alpha1.SandboxContainerResources{\n\t\t\tLimits: v1alpha1.SandboxResourceList{\n\t\t\t\tCPU:    v1alpha1.DefaultCPULimit,\n\t\t\t\tMemory: v1alpha1.DefaultMemoryLimit,\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t},\n\t\tEnv: []v1alpha1.SandboxEnvVar{\n\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\tName:  \"PYTHON_VERSION\",\n\t\t\t\tValue: \"3.11\",\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\tName: \"API_KEY\",\n\t\t\t\tValueFrom: &v1alpha1.SandboxEnvVarSource{\n\t\t\t\t\tSecretKeyRef: &v1alpha1.SandboxSecretKeyRef{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tName: \"api-secret\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\tKey:  \"key\",\n\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t},\n\t\tSecurityContext: &v1alpha1.SandboxSecurityContext{\n\t\t\tRunAsNonRoot: func() *bool { b := true; return &b }(),\n\t\t\tSeccompProfile: &v1alpha1.SandboxSeccompProfile{\n\t\t\t\tType: v1alpha1.SeccompProfileTypeRuntimeDefault,\n\t\t\t},\n\t\t},\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n### Resource Limits\n\nDefault resource limits should be:\n- Applied consistently across all interpreters\n- Configurable via CRD spec\n- Monitored for resource usage\n- Prevented from consuming cluster resources\n\n### Timeout Enforcement\n\nExecution timeouts should be:\n- Enforced by the PicoD daemon\n- Configurable per CodeInterpreter\n- Applied to all code execution requests\n- Validated against maximum allowed values\n\n### Environment Variable Security\n\nEnvironment variables from Secrets should:\n- Be encrypted at rest\n- Only be accessible to authorized service accounts\n- Be validated for sensitive patterns\n- Be rotated regularly\n\n### Runtime Type Validation\n\nRuntime types must be:\n- Explicitly enumerated\n- Validated at admission time\n- Restricted to approved languages\n- Monitored for security vulnerabilities\n\n## Future Enhancements\n\n### Potential Extensions\n\n1. **Custom Runtime Types**: Support for user-defined runtime configurations\n2. **Dynamic Resource Limits**: Per-request resource scaling\n3. **Namespace-level Defaults**: Namespace-specific default configurations\n4. **Resource Quotas**: Integration with Kubernetes resource quotas\n5. **Policy Enforcement**: Validation policies for runtime configurations\n6. **Metrics Integration**: Prometheus metrics for runtime usage\n\n### Version Migration Path\n\nFuture migration from v1alpha1 to v1beta1/v1:\n1. Create new constants file `pkg/apis/runtime/v1beta1/constants.go`\n2. Migrate shared types to new version\n3. Implement conversion functions between v1alpha1 and v1beta1\n4. Update CRD to serve both versions\n5. Set v1beta1 as storage version\n6. Update controllers and clients to use v1beta1\n7. Deprecate v1alpha1 after migration period","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-003/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":22,"character":1},"end":{"line":22,"character":7}},"severity":2,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://staticcheck.dev/docs/ch